title: Trailer Wiring Harness Install: CURT 56096 on a Cadillac SRX
description:
This video depicts the installation of the CURT 56096 T-Connector on a 2013 Cadillac SRX.

Install Sheet:
https://www.curtmfg.com/masterlibrary/56096/installsheet/CME_56096_INS.PDF

Application Coverage:
2010-2015 Cadillac SRX

Special Notes:
All Steps must be followed to ensure correct function of the T-Connector.  To verify proper installation once installed, test by connecting a test light or properly wired trailer.

Warning:
-This video is intended to be used as reference. Please refer to print instructions for complete installation information.
tags: CURT Trailer wiring, how to install, towing, curt 56096, Cadillac SRX
